chapter 1 of title 3, United States Code, is amended\*-
.uu
(1)  by striking out the item relating to section 21 and inserting in lieu
thereof the following:
.ss
.ft R
.q "22.  Definitions." "; and"
.uu
(2) by inserting after the item relating to section 20 the following new item:
.ss
.ft R
.q "21.  Single poll closing time in continental United States." .
.tt
(b)  AMENDMENTS TO UNIFORM TIME ACT OF 1966.\*-Section 3(a) of the Uniform
Time Act of 1966 (15 U.S.C. 260a(a)) is amended by striking out
.q "2 o'clock antemeridian"
each place it appears and inserting in lieu thereof
.q "2:00 o'clock ante meridiem" .
